<Layout 
  title="Web Applications - Cloud Intelligence"
  description="Build modern, scalable web applications with cutting-edge technologies and user-centric design."
  keywords="web applications, progressive web apps, e-commerce, SaaS, API development, mobile-first"
>
  <PageHero 
    title="Web Applications"
    subtitle="Modern Digital Experiences"
    description="Create powerful, scalable web applications that engage users and drive business growth with cutting-edge technologies."
  />
  
  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2>Transform Your Digital Presence</h2>
        <p>
          Our web application development services combine modern frameworks, cloud-native architecture, 
          and user-centered design to create applications that scale with your business. From startup MVPs 
          to enterprise platforms, we deliver solutions that perform exceptionally across all devices and environments.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="features-grid">
        {features.map((feature) => (
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">{feature.icon}</div>
            <h3>{feature.title}</h3>
            <p>{feature.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready to Build Your Web Application?</h2>
        <p>Transform your ideas into powerful digital experiences</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What web development technologies do you use?</h3>
          <p>We work with modern frameworks including React, Vue.js, Angular, Next.js, and Astro for frontend development. For backend, we use Node.js, Python (Django, FastAPI), and cloud-native technologies. We select the best technology stack based on your specific requirements and scalability needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How long does web application development take?</h3>
          <p>Simple web applications take 4-8 weeks, medium complexity projects require 8-16 weeks, and enterprise-level applications typically take 3-6 months. Timeline depends on features, integrations, custom design requirements, and testing scope. We provide detailed project timelines during planning.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you develop mobile-responsive web applications?</h3>
          <p>Yes, all our web applications are built with mobile-first responsive design principles. They work seamlessly across desktop, tablet, and mobile devices with optimized performance, touch-friendly interfaces, and consistent user experiences regardless of screen size.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can you integrate with existing systems and APIs?</h3>
          <p>Absolutely. We specialize in integrating web applications with existing CRMs, ERPs, payment gateways, third-party APIs, and legacy systems. We ensure secure data flow, maintain system compatibility, and implement proper authentication and authorization protocols.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What security measures do you implement?</h3>
          <p>We implement comprehensive security including HTTPS encryption, input validation, SQL injection prevention, XSS protection, CSRF tokens, secure authentication (OAuth, JWT), data encryption, security headers, and regular security audits. All applications follow OWASP security guidelines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you provide ongoing maintenance and support?</h3>
          <p>Yes, we offer comprehensive maintenance packages including security updates, performance monitoring, bug fixes, feature enhancements, backup management, and 24/7 support. We ensure your web application remains secure, fast, and up-to-date with evolving technologies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

